//        <4=> 4: 100 = 32-bit CRC-32 (X32 + X26 + X23 + X22 + X16 + X12 + X11 +X10 + X8 + X7 + X5 + X4 + X2 + X + 1)
//        <5=> 5: Others = No calculation is executed
//        <6=> 6: Others = No calculation is executed
