//        <1=> 1: 1 = An interrupt request is generated on the falling edge of the 9th clock cycle. Master mode: After the output of nine clock pulses, the clock output is set to the low level and clock stretching is set. Slave mode: After the input of 9 clock pulses, the clock is set to the low level and clock stretching is set for the master device.
//    </combo>
